    {"id":"t4","type":"text","x":1365,"y":130,"width":250,"height":480,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#9a3412","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":["g4"],"roundness":null,"seed":9022,"version":1,"versionNonce":9022,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"④ 反馈层｜回写 + 验收\n\n统一回写：\n- Deliverable\n- Feishu Link\n- GitHub Link\n- Owner/Status/Next\n\n执行节奏：\n- 实时进展即回写\n- EOD只做汇总\n\n管理收益：\n- 看板可诊断\n- 交付可追溯\n- 复盘可复用\n\n一句话：\n“不是只聊流程，\n而是交付持续推进。”","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":16,"containerId":null,"originalText":"④ 反馈层｜回写 + 验收\n\n统一回写：\n- Deliverable\n- Feishu Link\n- GitHub Link\n- Owner/Status/Next\n\n执行节奏：\n- 实时进展即回写\n- EOD只做汇总\n\n管理收益：\n- 看板可诊断\n- 交付可追溯\n- 复盘可复用\n\n一句话：\n“不是只聊流程，\n而是交付持续推进。”","lineHeight":1.25}
